import React from "react";
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, Form, FormControl } from "react-bootstrap";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import { FaAmbulance } from "react-icons/fa"; // ✅ Ambulance symbol

function AppNavbar() {
  return (
    <Navbar
      expand="lg"
      style={{ backgroundColor: "#f28b82" }} // ✅ Light red background
      variant="dark"
    >
      <Container>
        {/* Left: Logo and Title */}
        <Navbar.Brand as={Link} to="/home" style={{ color: "#fff", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
          <FaAmbulance style={{ marginRight: "8px" }} />
          Emergency System
        </Navbar.Brand>

        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbarScroll" />

        <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">
          {/* Center: Search Bar */}
          <Form className="mx-auto" style={{ width: "50%" }}>
            <FormControl
              type="search"
              placeholder="Search"
              className="me-2"
              aria-label="Search"
              style={{ borderRadius: "20px" }}
            />
          </Form>

          {/* Right: Nav Links */}
          <Nav className="ms-auto my-2 my-lg-0" navbarScroll>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/home" style={{ color: "#fff" }}>
              Home
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/register" style={{ color: "#fff" }}>
              Register
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/profile" style={{ color: "#fff" }}>
              My Profile
            </Nav.Link>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default AppNavbar;
